ROAD BLASTERS:

        On the starting line, type "LAVILLASTRANGIATO" and use the 
        following keys:

            'X'___________SPINS CAR.    '1'_____MOUNT VZ CANNONS.
            'S'__________NEXT STAGE.    '2'______CRUISE MISSILES.
            'F'______________REFUEL.    '3'_______ELECTRO SHIELD.
            'G'____________END GAME.    '4'______NITRO INJECTORS.
                        '0'_____REMOVES WEAPONS.

